      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-14/will-iran-s-attack-on-israel-spark-wider-a-middle-east-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员及其盟友现在正集中精力确保以色列的任何报复行动不会导致风险过高。]]></description>
